text: Novobakayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Bakayevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 65 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Kushnarenkovo, 7 km from Bakayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Novobakayevo, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
